      "verse": 43,
      "speaker": "श्रीभगवान्",
      "slok": "ॐ तत्सदिति श्रीमद्भगवद्गीतासूपनिषत्सु\nब्रह्मविद्यायां योगशास्त्रे श्रीकृष्णार्जुनसंवादे\nविभूतियोगो नाम दशमोऽध्यायः ||१०||",
      "transliteration": "OM tatsaditi śrīmadbhagavadgītāsūpaniṣatsu brahmavidyāyāṃ yogaśāstre śrīkṛṣṇārjunasaṃvāde vibhūtiyogo nāma daśamo.adhyāyaḥ ||10-43||",
      "translation_hi": "Swami Tejomayananda did not comment on this sloka",
      "translation_en": "Swami Sivananda did not comment on this sloka",
